@label fresnel_sine
    Fresnel Sine Integral:

    $ \fn{S}(x) = \int_0^x
      \sin\left(\frac{\pi t^2}{2}\right) dt $

    Taylor expansion:

    $ \fn{S}(x) = \sum_{n=0}^\infty
      \frac{(-1)^n \left(\pi / 2\right)^{2n+1} x^{4n+3}}
      {(4n+3)(2n+1)!} $

    TODO: Use Cassilda (A Hyades file processor), it rocks!\\
    TODO: Document more obscure functions.
@end

@cassilda: fresnel_sine
